PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776874270
OL,3,CDriver, 69, guilty of killing Take
OL,4,CThat fan on her way to Bristol gig
OL,6,FInvestigating officer Noelie Poupard
OL,7,Ffrom the Serious Collision
OL,8,FInvestigation Team at Avon and
OL,9,FSomerset Police said: "This was an
OL,10,Fincredibly tragic incident which
OL,11,Fresulted in the death of a much-loved
OL,12,Fdaughter, wife and friend who was on
OL,13,Fher way out to enjoy her evening with
OL,14,Fher friends.
OL,26,@qD@WOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776874270
OL,3,CDriver, 69, guilty of killing Take
OL,4,CThat fan on her way to Bristol gig
OL,6,F"It was the defence's case that Hodge
OL,7,Fhad suffered an epileptic seizure at
OL,8,Fthe time of the collision, however it
OL,9,Fappears the jury rejected this idea
OL,10,Fand felt her lack of care and
OL,11,Fattention is what caused Mrs
OL,12,FCrossman's death.
OL,14,F"Mrs Crossman's family have endured a
OL,15,Fgreat deal of pain over the past 18
OL,16,Fmonths and they have shown great
OL,17,Fstrength and dignity throughout the
OL,18,Finvestigation and trial. My hope is
OL,19,Fthat this result give them some
OL,20,Fclosure."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@IO]
